---
const logos = [
  { name: "Allan Gray Orbis Foundation", src: "/logos/allan-gray-orbis-foundation.avif" },
  { name: "4Di Capital", src: "/logos/4di-capital.avif" },
  { name: "Knife Capital", src: "/logos/knife-venture-capital.avif" },
  { name: "Newtown Partners", src: "/logos/newtonton-partners.avif" },
  { name: "Kalon Venture Partners", src: "/logos/kalon-venture-partners.avif" },
  { name: "FNB Ventures / FirstRand", src: "/logos/fnb-small-business-investments.avif" },
  { name: "Nedbank Small Business", src: "/logos/Pitch-and-Polish-Logo.png" },
  { name: "Standard Bank SME", src: "/logos/standard-bank-summit.avif" },
  // Add more if you want (e.g. IDC, Savant, etc.)
];
---

<section class="bg-zinc-950 py-16 text-white overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <!-- Headline -->
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
      Are you investor-ready and funding-ready?
    </h2>

    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
      Most founders jump straight to pitching investors without completing this essential checklist 
      and <span class="text-amber-400 font-medium">yet still fail</span> in front of the panel.
    </p>

    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-zinc-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">
      We refine your story, strengthen your numbers, and position you to stand out when it matters most.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA Button -->
    <a 
      href="#invite" 
      class="inline-block bg-white text-black font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg hover:bg-amber-400 hover:text-black transition-all duration-300"
    >
      Get the Investor-Ready Checklist
    </a>

    <!-- Closing Question -->
    <p class="mt-12 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-amber-400">
      Your investors are ready to back you — are you?
      <br>We are not affiliated with any specific investor, we prepare you to confidently pitch to:
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Infinite Logo Marquee -->
  <div class="mt-20">
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Gradient overlays for smooth fade effect -->
      <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-zinc-950 to-transparent z-10"></div>
      <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-20 bg-gradient-to-l from-zinc-950 to-transparent z-10"></div>

      <div class="overflow-hidden">
        <div 
          class="flex items-center gap-16 md:gap-24 whitespace-nowrap animate-marquee"
        >
          {logos.concat(logos).map((logo) => (
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center opacity-75 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
              <img 
                src={logo.src} 
                alt={logo.name}
                class="h-10 md:h-12 w-auto grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <span class="text-[10px] text-zinc-500 mt-2 tracking-widest">{logo.name}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes marquee {
    from {
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
    to {
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }
  }

  .animate-marquee {
    animation: marquee 5s linear infinite;
    will-change: transform;
  }

  /* Pause on hover (optional - remove if you want completely non-stop) */
  .animate-marquee:hover {
    animation-play-state: paused;
  }
</style>